These are Puzzles for 4x7 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 4x7-Level-1-1::.
The people grow 7 different varities of flowers: daisy, zinnia, tulip, dahlia, orchid, iris, sunflower
The people prefer 7 different music-genres: ambient, blues, classical, disco, folk, house, salsa
The people have 7 different jobs:  musician, engineer, nurse, firefighter, teacher, software-developer, mechanic
The people perfer 7 different movie-genres: drama, zombie, horror, spy, scientific, mystery, crime
 1. the person who growsdaisy is on the left of the person who growssunflower##1
 2. the fan of disco is on the right of the musician##1
 3. the person watching drama movies is the teacher##1
 4. the teacher is on the right of the engineer##1
 5. the fan of salsa is on the far left##1
 6. the person watching horror movies is on the right of the fan of house##1
 7. the fan of blues is on the right of the person who growsdahlia##1
 8. the person watching zombie movies is on the right of the person watching scientific movies##1
 9. the fan of classical is on the far right##1
10. the fan of classical is on the right of the person watching scientific movies##1
11. the person who growsiris is in the middle##1
12. the person who growstulip is on the far left##1
13. the fan of folk is in the middle##1
14. the software-developer is on the left of the nurse##1
15. the person watching crime movies is on the left of the person who growsdaisy##1
16. the teacher is on the left of the software-developer##1
17. the person watching mystery movies is on the right of the person watching crime movies##1
18. the fan of classical is on the right of the firefighter##1
19. the person watching horror movies is in the middle##1
20. the firefighter is on the left of the person who growszinnia##1
21. the fan of blues is on the right of the person who growsdahlia##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |   3    |     4      |    5     |     6      |       7       |
| Flower      | tulip    | daisy     | sunflower  | iris   | dahlia | orchid      | zinnia          |
| Music-Genre   | salsa    | disco   | house  | folk       | ambient  | blues      | classical     |
| Job         | musician | engineer | teacher | software-developer | nurse   | firefighter     | mechanic |
| Movie-Genre     | crime      | mystery   | drama   | horror  | spy  | scientific | zombie       |

