 6. the prince-smoker is on the far left##1
 7. the person traveling to hamburg is on the right of the person drinking juice##1
 8. the siglo-smoker is the freelancer##1
 9. the person drinking lemonade is the coach##1
10. the person traveling to paris is in the middle##1
11. the coach is on the right of the person drinking milk##1
12. the person traveling to marseilles is the person drinking water##1
13. the person traveling to san-francisco is on the left of the person traveling to hamburg##1
14. the person drinking sprite is on the right of the siglo-smoker##1
15. the engineer is on the right of the social-worker##1
16. the person traveling to marseilles is the person drinking water##1
17. the fonseca-smoker is on the right of the dancer##1
18. the person traveling to hamburg is on the left of the person traveling to london##1
