 1. the owner of the hedgehog is on the left of the person driving the bus##1
 2. the person driving the taxi is on the right of the person who's birthday is in august##1
 3. the owner of the turtle is on the right of the person driving the train##1
 4. the person who's birthday is in january is on the left of the person who's birthday is in february##1
