 7. the person eating cabbage is in the middle##1
 8. the person who's birthday is in july is on the left of the owner of the hedgehog##1
 9. the person eating cucumber is on the right of the person who's birthday is in july##1
10. the person eating avocado is on the right of the owner of the ferret##1
11. the person driving the train is on the right of the owner of the frog##1
12. the person eating cabbage is on the left of the owner of the frog##1
13. the person eating avocado is on the far right##1
14. the person who's birthday is in march is the person eating avocado##1
15. the person driving the bus is the owner of the goldfish##1
16. the person eating februarysy is on the left of the person who's birthday is in august##1
17. the owner of the pony is on the left of the person eating lettuce##1
18. the owner of the guinea-pig is the person driving the quad-bike##1
19. the person who's birthday is in july is on the left of the person driving the subway##1
20. the person driving the scooter is on the far left##1
